Reentrancy in MusiconomiCrowdsale.claimCofounditTokens (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#414-420):
	External calls:
	- token.mintTokens(cofounditAddress,cofounditReward) (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- cofounditHasClaimedTokens (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol)

Reentrancy in MusiconomiCrowdsale.claimCoreTeamsTokens (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#400-413):
	External calls:
	- devReward = maxTokenSupply - token.totalSupply() (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#405-408)
	- token.mintTokens(_to,devReward) (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#410)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- ownerHasClaimedTokens (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#411)

Reentrancy in MusiconomiCrowdsale.processTransaction (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#274-303):
	External calls:
	- token.mintTokens(_contributor,tokenAmount) (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#296-300)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- contributorList (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#300-302)

MusiconomiCrowdsale.salvageTokensFromContract (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#329-336) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-IERC20Token(_tokenAddress).transfer(_to,_amount) (/unique_chucks/5/0xb9e0fc2a1c9d567af555e07e72f27e686f2c6872.sol#333-335)

MusiconomiCrowdsale.batchReturnEthIfFailed has external calls inside a loop:
